324
00:17:42,564 --> 00:17:43,963
Yeah.

325
00:17:43,964 --> 00:17:46,663
Second of all, about establishing the alibi.

326
00:17:46,664 --> 00:17:50,663
Perhaps this criminal act was a compulsive one.

327
00:17:50,664 --> 00:17:54,063
Thus the murderer was not well-prepared, I assume.

328
00:17:54,064 --> 00:17:57,263
