361
00:19:45,764 --> 00:19:48,863
It was Mr. Ohkubo's last message to you,

362
00:19:48,864 --> 00:19:52,264
whom he treated like his own child.

363
00:19:54,864 --> 00:19:57,163
Mr. Ohkubo said to you,

364
00:19:57,164 --> 00:20:00,663
Mizuhara, smile. Smile is your new style.

365
00:20:00,664 --> 00:20:03,264
You look amazing when you smile.

366
00:20:07,964 --> 00:20:09,763
I didn't know that.

367
00:20:09,764 --> 00:20:10,963
This can't be true!

368
00:20:10,964 --> 00:20:12,763
Who in the world would encourage someone

369
00:20:12,764 --> 00:20:14,863
